## About

This is a simple yet powerful web-based expense tracking application designed to help users monitor and manage their personal spending habits. With a clean and intuitive interface, the app allows users to log daily expenses, categorize them, and gain insights into their financial behavior over time.

Built as a personal project, the goal is to provide a lightweight tool thatâ€™s easy to use while remaining flexible enough for future enhancements like budgeting tools, visual analytics, and smart spending insights. Whether you're tracking monthly bills or everyday purchases, this app aims to support better financial awareness with minimal friction.

